                <h2>Mistborn</h2>
                <p class="author">Brandon Sanderson</p>
                <p><i>Mistborn</i> was a life-changer for me. Never before had I read a story so enthralling, with characters
                so well written. Every character is unique and memorable and act like real people would in their place.
                The magic system is so unique and flesh-out that it feels real. This first book is a landmark in fantasy
                literature, but the following books in the series are just as excellent. Sanderson has a unique gift to
                realize excellent characters, beautiful systems, and worlds that evolve and progress through the story naturally.
                    He is easily one of my favorite authors and <i>Mistborn</i> is one of my favorite books of all time.</p>
