                <p>What can I say about the father of all modern fantasy that hasn't already been said? Tolkien's <i>Lord of
                the Rings</i> is a power-house of excellence. Though I did not read the books until after I had seen
                Peter Jackson's film adaptaion of the first part, after I had, I was hooked. <i>Lord of the Rings</i> is,
